    "description": "Annual baseline (upgrade_id=0) restricted via applied_in=[1] — buildings where upgrade 1 applied successfully. Validator was relaxed in 2026-04-26 commit (e85e741) to allow applied_in on baseline queries; before that, the validator rejected this combination as 'applied_in cannot be set when applied_only is False'. Pins the SQL shape that test_savings_equals_independent_baseline_minus_upgrade depends on.",
